;Current Special Effects
;1 - Regeneration (+75 life every second)
;2 - Armor (-25% damage taken, -50% speed)
;3 - Berserk (+50% damage given AND taken, +10 Attack Rate)
;4 - Anti-Projectile (Can't be hit by projectiles)
;5 - Evasion (When hit, 10% chance -33% damage, 10% chance -66% damage, 10% chance -100% damage)
;6 - X Berserk (+250% damage dealt, -80% Life)
;7 - Recon (-50% Max Life, +50% Speed, slowly restores Enemy Strength Meter)
;8 - EX Bomb (3 Grenades are dropped upon defeat)
;9 - Jammer (Enemy HUD area becomes covered with a black 'fuzz')
;10 = Barrier (Start with semi-random strength barrier that resists weak attacks)
;11 = Stealth (Hard to spot. Increased damage when attacking out of stealth)
;12 = Sub-Elite (+10% damage dealt, +25% Max Life)
;13 = Elite (+20% damage dealt, +50% Max Life, +10 Attack Rate)
;14 = Super-Elite (+30% damage dealt, +75% Max Life, +20 Attack Rate, +15% Speed)
;15 = Stagger (When taking damage, 60% of damage is delayed, instead being taken over time at a rate of 10 damage a second.)

